    <p>About Tapestry5 Portlet application ...</p>
	
	<p>
	This library is based on work of Markus Feindler, Le Xuan Trun and Kristina B. Taylor 
	(see <a href="http://code.google.com/p/tapestry5portlet/">project</a> for more details).<br/> 
	Like Felix Scheffer (<a href="http://code.google.com/p/tapestry5-portlet-support/">project</a> for more details), 
	we have updated the dependencies of this library to use Tapestry 5.2.6.
	</p>
	<p>
	This library support:
	<ul>
		<li>portlet event processing (JSR 286)</li>
		<li> serving ajax request as resource </li>  
		<li> support MARKUP_HEAD_ELEMENT </li>
		<li> use of Apache Pluto to ease the test of portlet features </li>
	</ul>
	</p> 
	
		
	<p>
	Code is available at <a href="https://github.com/got5/tapestry5-portlet">GOT5</a>	
	for more details check also https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/TAP5-64
	</p>
		
